Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.70,0:00:12.23,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.21,0:00:18.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,照亮了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:30.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.06,0:00:37.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.10,0:00:45.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:52.34,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.41,0:01:01.12,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.19,0:01:06.59,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.66,0:01:11.53,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.60,0:01:16.47,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:24.01,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.11,0:01:27.34,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,37尼欧皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟我来 娜蒂亚公主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要带你去见一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.27,0:01:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼欧皇帝陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我将娜蒂亚公主带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就是娜蒂亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.82,0:02:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蔚蓝之水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.95,0:02:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是父王的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼欧皇帝陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了新亚特兰提斯的复活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请您助我等一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.80,0:02:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,找到红色诺亚了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,于PX703 旧亚特兰提斯帝国遗址发现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它果然是潜沉至 那座垃圾山之上是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那才不是垃圾山 是神圣的墓园
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,坟墓对活着的人 一点用处都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.82,0:03:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讲到垃圾 尼莫的船情况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根据回报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,旧塔提苏司遗址 没有任何能源与生命迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该已经溶解蒸发掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希望他们能走的顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.41,0:03:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好惊人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到非洲大陆下方 竟然有这样的隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不只是非洲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,五大洲七大洋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到处都开凿了 这样的子弹隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这也是古代亚特兰提斯人 建造的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,失去浮力的旧鹦鹉螺号 能够逃过一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也都要多亏有海底洋流 带我们到这座隧道来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是古代亚特兰提斯人万万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不管怎么说 我们也因此得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.17,0:04:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来只剩下救出娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再解决那艘空中战舰就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 事情并没有那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得到蔚蓝之水的石像鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将会去启动他梦寐以求的 红色诺亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的目的该不会是红色诺亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是艘能让全世界 再次遵循亚特兰提斯秩序的神舟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么 就让我带你前往 另一艘诺亚方舟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得到红色诺亚的石像鬼 将会执行最终计划
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,首先是对全世界宣战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:04:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么会呢 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为这个地球没有武器 能胜过红色诺亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,违逆者将遭到神的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,愚蠢的人们 根本无法靠近这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在的人类并没有 战胜红色诺亚的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唯一的希望是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,同样以亚特兰提斯的超科学 创造出来的这艘船舰对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 这艘船的机能尚不完全
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,主要引擎仍未检测完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毕竟它已经在地底 封印了1万2千多年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 只要主机能顺利运转
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定就能飞上天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飞？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船在空中飞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船以及红色诺亚 原本都是太空船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太空船？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两艘都是在240万年前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:06:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古代亚特兰提斯人 迫降地球成功后仅存的太空船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 之前的鹦鹉螺号 原本也是太空船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那红色诺亚里面的那个也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 那是小型太空船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它的同型舰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第二世代型行星间航行用 亚光速太空船『爱顿琉姆』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是旧鹦鹉螺号的前身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱顿琉姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这么说 那时的板子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 太空船时代留下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 就算这艘船能飞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它有能力和那个 超大的红色诺亚对抗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船舰以前的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第四世代型超光速 恒星间航行用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,超特级万能宇宙战舰 『艾格希里昂』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和红色诺亚同样是以 奥菲斯型大型缩退炉为主引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那成对消灭引擎呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成对消灭引擎 只是这艘船的辅助引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用来转动飞轮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那只是用来辅助…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使是成对消灭引擎的强大威力 也无法胜过红色诺亚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个世界上能够战胜缩退炉的 就只有缩退炉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等我 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.86,0:07:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一定会去救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟我来 娜蒂亚公主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我来带你参观这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,代替你已经过世的父王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你觉得你身上的服装如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我连尺寸都调查得一清二楚 这可是特地为了公主而订制的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还满意吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么可能会满意 丢脸死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这可真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我本人倒是非常满意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你晓得这是什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人的手…巨人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是由古代亚特兰提斯人 创造出来的最早人类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亚当
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亚当？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是旧约圣经所记载的 神所创造的最初人类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个是人类？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这只是试作品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当时还无法缩小体型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,后来经过不断改良
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才变成今日的大小
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那所谓的人类不就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们亚特兰提斯人创造出来 用来当作仆人的生命体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,距今240万年前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来到地球的亚特兰提斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,首先想到的就是要创造出 对自己忠诚的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为他们的数量实在太少了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:09:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最初是试着选择在生物中 智能较高的鲸鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但似乎不太顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 其末裔 仍有极少数存活至今
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,南极的伊里恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错 原来你晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,记取失败的教训 他们后来改用了猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了使用起来更方便
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,于是给予它们较高的智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.82,0:09:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尽可能地参照他们自己 也就是亚特兰提斯人的外表
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,创造出了人类
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这么说 我们人类 并不是从猴子进化的生物吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你知道『缺环』这个词吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,缺环？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 就是失落的环节
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然大家都说 人类是从小小的猴子进化来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是为什么能从猴子 转变成人类呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么人类的身体 会不再长出长毛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能够使用工具 学会用语言沟通呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,至今仍未有人能解开这个谜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将猴子与人类 连结在一起的进化环节
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在就是缺少那个环节
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果那个环节 是亚特兰提斯人做出来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 人类的进化就解释得通了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 要怎样才能从猿猴身上 制造出我们人类呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就是靠…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,基因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,基因？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.92,0:10:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用来创造出地球人 就是类似设计图的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而做出这种设计的 就是古代亚特兰提斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尚未完成的人类 以及制作失败的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里可说是间人类博物馆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太过份了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:10:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才这么点小事就被吓到 实在很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们亚特兰提斯人 是他们的造物主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,同时也是饲主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚公主也要有自觉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谁理你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,话可别说得太满
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？娜蒂亚公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你没有话要说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么可能会有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那可不行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了增进彼此的了解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我希望能和你聊聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与其助纣为虐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我倒情愿死了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别说出那么伤人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.18,0:11:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今后你将和我一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:12:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别跟我意气用事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.85,0:12:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我最讨厌你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我被讨厌了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.55,0:12:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比起同样身为 亚特兰提斯人的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你似乎更喜欢人类
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不会去跟人类 一起生活看看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也跟尼莫说了同样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然相隔两地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.77,0:12:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但不愧是父女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你还没有回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 你好好看清楚人类
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.51,0:12:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使是同类
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要是自己排斥的对象 就毫不留情地歧视
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只想着保护自己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肤浅狭隘的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更何况你可是个外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们是不可能接纳你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人类根本没有改进的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们是制造失败的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,需要我们这些主人来管理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:12:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然可悲 但这就是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再说 我可没兴趣 跟家畜住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.88,0:13:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以你才不把杀人当一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要使用 从我身上抢走的蔚蓝之水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成为恶魔对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说错了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,皇帝陛下是即将成为神的 蔚蓝之水正统继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蔚蓝之水是父亲传承给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,13年前的那个时候 是我放你逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我终究还是狠不下心 杀死自己的亲妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能够像这样再次重逢 或许是命运的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可悲的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.64,0:14:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只想毁灭你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别白费力气了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一定会办到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死了这条心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的命是我救的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不希望杀死你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,皇帝陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即将抵达巴黎上空
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请您预作准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.23,0:14:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就跟我一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了让你了解自己的立场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,（巴黎7：00AM）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.37,0:14:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吾乃新亚特兰提斯帝国皇帝 尼欧·伊肯·艾皮法尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我向全世界的人类宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们才是人类的造物主 （伦敦6：00AM）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是你们真正的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.85,0:15:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因此 命令你们再次臣服 （万里长城2：00PM）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不愿臣服者将以死来偿其罪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.59,0:15:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今后诸位 （纽约1：01AM）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,须服从新亚特兰提斯之命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只能以 新亚特兰提斯之仆役身分自居
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了让那些分不清事实的 愚昧之人认清现实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在此展现神罚之光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,（亚利桑那12：01AM）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,（夏威夷群岛8：01PM）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,首先 先交出英国这个小国吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从现在算起的24小时内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将白旗高挂于艾菲尔铁塔 以示投降
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若有不从
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,届时我将给予伦敦神的制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,终于开始行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是真的想和全世界开战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这到底是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,世界末日要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:16:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是再这样下去会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,缩退炉已经完成检测
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船办得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加上凯撒琳也已经改造完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再说 古今中外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.39,0:17:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一向是邪不胜正
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.33,0:17:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 你思考的方式错了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们不属于恶 而是善的那方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你太傲慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们是为了拯救 走错方向的愚蠢人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好意将他们引导至正途
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若不由我们 亚特兰提斯人来管理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.15,0:17:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人类迟早会自取灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而那些亚特兰提斯人 才一天一夜就毁灭了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是人类却还存活到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亚特兰提斯人是不灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为他们的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:17:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由我继承了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,差不多要请你也来帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢各位陪伴我到今日 （静冈县吹合岬）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 再往下走 各位可能都将难逃一死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们不需要如此牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好好留在地球上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最后我只想说一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.20,0:18:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别跟来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.07,0:19:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 你要留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去找个好男人结婚生子 把孩子抚养长大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们会去建立一个 让大家能安居乐业的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.52,0:19:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爷爷
