Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们会在英国等你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉 我去去就回
