Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
