Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该不会是…\N该不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.23,0:23:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.00,0:23:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.41,0:23:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就是不肯让我好过是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.35,0:23:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.01,0:23:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来解决一切恩怨的时候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.42,0:23:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石像鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.12,0:23:55.65,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
